Trendkite, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 9:57 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Trendkite, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Trendkite, Inc. provides PR and media monitoring software to agencies and corporate brands to help measure and analyze the impact of their PR efforts across multiple channels with minimal effort. It offers users a set of metrics to measure PR’s brand, marketing, and bottom-line impact. The company’s media monitoring tools provides a single, comprehensive view of coverage across media types, including traditional news, blogs, print, broadcast, radio, and even premium paywall subscriptions. It also offers interactive PR reports for actionable media analysis. Trendkite, Inc. was founded in 2012 and is based in Austin, Texas.


800 Brazos StreetSuite 340Austin, TX 78701United StatesFounded in 2012



Phone: 512-298-0100

www.trendkite.com







