Product Overview
TrendKite helps brands and agencies quantify and amplify the impact of their PR efforts by easily creating a timely, precise picture of their brand's media coverage.




Features


                                            Automated, Interactive Reports - With one click you can transform your media dashboards into beautiful, interactive reports you can share with your team.
                                        

                                            Custom Media Dashboards - Easily measure the impact of news on your brand with custom dashboards displaying the media metrics that matter most to you.
                                        

                                            News Alerts - We deliver a comprehensive group of relevant news items to your inbox every morning.
                                        

                                            News Monitoring Dashboard - We provide you with the most impactful mentions by using our proprietary impact score to filter your news.
                                        


Purpose


                                    TrendKite uses advanced semantic analysis and sophisticated big data analytics to model the PR ecosystem. Because TrendKite understands the publications, their audiences, their authors, their subject areas and the brands they mention, our users don't have to join the keyword guessing game or miss fleeting opportunities for coverage.
                                







